FBIS4-51973 "dreas087_c_94022" FBIS-EAS-94-087 Daily Report 1 May 1994 NORTHEAST ASIA North Korea Peruvian Party Secretary, Entourage Feted Peruvian Party Secretary, Entourage Feted SK0105085694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0829 GMT 1 May 94 SK0105085694 Pyongyang KCNA English BFN [Text] Pyongyang, May 1 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] gave a reception Saturday in honor of Secretary of the National Executive Committee of the American Popular Revolutionary Alliance of Peru Javier Pedro and his entourage on a visit to Korea. Present at the reception were Hwang Chang-yop, secretary of the WPK Central Committee, and officials concerned.
